description: Erection of a part 3 part 5 part 6 part 8 and part 10 storey building to provide 77 residential units (19 x 1 bed 32 x 2 bed 20 x 3 bed and 6 x 4 bed) and 5879 square metres (GEA) of B1 (office) floor space together with 46 car parking spaces and 70 cycle spaces at basement level and demolition of the existing buildings.
